FROM debian:stable

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      make \
      libxml-treebuilder-perl \
      libyaml-libyaml-perl \

      libjson-xs-perl \

    && apt install --no-install-recommends /tmp/dnscontrol.deb -y

WORKDIR /dns
ADD . .

VOLUME ["/dns/data"]

CMD ["make", "check"]
